Class Magazine

  • java.lang.Object
    • magazine_service.Magazine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Magazine
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Magazine class represents a weekly personalized magazine. It contains details about the main part cost and supplements offered.
